        "text": "=Draft a concise, professional reply offering 3 specific time slots.\n\nOriginal subject: {{ $json.subject }}\nSender first name: {{ $json.sender_name }}\nOriginal message (for context, do not quote):\n{{ $json.body }}\n\nProposed slots (already filtered against my calendar, in my timezone):\n{{ $json.slotsText }}\n\nWrite the reply body only — no greeting line beyond \"Hi {{ $json.sender_name }},\", no signature (it will be appended by Gmail). 3 short paragraphs max. Offer the slots as a numbered list. End with: \"If none of these work, share a couple of windows that suit you.\"",
